{
  "id": "69b32dd21ccfde6acd7e46bd",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:原理主義へのカウンター",
  "created": 1773350386,
  "updated": 1773350402,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b32dd21ccfde6acd7e46bd",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:原理主義へのカウンター",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350386,
      "updated": 1773350386
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df20000000000284a6d",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350386,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a6e",
      "text": "やほやほ〜。今日のテーマは「[原理主義へのカウンター]」ね！ちょっとムズそうだけど、要するに「これが絶対正しい！他は全部ダメ！」みたいな考え方にどう向き合うか、って話だよね。ネットでもよく見るじゃん、そういうの。いわゆる「過激派オタク思考」っていうか…ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a6f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a70",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a71",
      "text": "ええ、とても大切なお話ですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a72",
      "text": "人は誰しも、自分の信じるものを大切にいたします。でも、その思いが強くなりすぎると、まるで固い殻のように、他の声が耳に届かなくなってしまうこともあります。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a73",
      "text": "そうしたとき、どうやって穏やかに風通しをよくするか……それが「[カウンター]」なのかもしれませんね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a74",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a75",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a76",
      "text": "定義を簡潔にしておく。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a77",
      "text": "[** [原理主義]（[fundamentalism]）]とは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a78",
      "text": " 特定の教義や思想を絶対的に正しいものとみなす",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a79",
      "text": " 異なる価値観を排除する傾向を持つ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a7a",
      "text": "という思考パターン。宗教だけではなく、政治、文化、ネットコミュニティでも観測される。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a7b",
      "text": "参考:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a7c",
      "text": "https://www.britannica.com/topic/fundamentalism",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a7d",
      "text": "対抗する方法は複数ある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a7e",
      "text": "大きくは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a7f",
      "text": " 1. [対話]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a80",
      "text": " 2. [教育]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a81",
      "text": " 3. [多様なコミュニティの形成]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a82",
      "text": "このあたりが典型だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a83",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a84",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a85",
      "text": "おおー、さすが技術担当りか氏。まとめ早いｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a86",
      "text": "でもさ、ネット見てるとさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a87",
      "text": "「対話しよう！」って言っても 全然会話成立しない人 いるじゃん？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a88",
      "text": "なんていうか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a89",
      "text": "「俺の正義100％、お前0％」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a8a",
      "text": "みたいな人。あれどうすんの？って思うんだよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a8b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a8c",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a8d",
      "text": "そういう方に出会うと、胸が少し痛みますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a8e",
      "text": "きっとその方も、何かを守ろうとしていらっしゃるのでしょう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a8f",
      "text": "人は、不安や恐れがあるとき、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a90",
      "text": "「これだけが正しい」と強く握りしめてしまうことがあります。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a91",
      "text": "ですから……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a92",
      "text": "「あなたの考えは間違っています」と正面から否定するよりも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a93",
      "text": "「その考えに至ったお気持ちは、どんなものだったのでしょう」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a94",
      "text": "と、やさしく問いかけるほうが、心の扉が少し開くこともあると思うのです。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a95",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a96",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a97",
      "text": "あーそれわかる！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a98",
      "text": "いきなり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a99",
      "text": "「お前それデマｗ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a9a",
      "text": "って言われたら、誰でもムカつくもんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a9b",
      "text": "防御モード入るやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a9c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a9d",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a9e",
      "text": "その点は研究でも指摘されている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284a9f",
      "text": "[バックファイア効果]と呼ばれる現象だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aa0",
      "text": "誤情報を訂正されると、逆に元の信念が強化されることがある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aa1",
      "text": "参考:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aa2",
      "text": "https://effectivethinking.org/backfire-effect",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aa3",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aa4",
      "text": "「論破」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aa5",
      "text": "→ 相手の態度を硬化させる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aa6",
      "text": "可能性がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aa7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aa8",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aa9",
      "text": "うわー、まじでネット論争あるあるじゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aaa",
      "text": "論破動画とかめっちゃバズるけど、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aab",
      "text": "説得にはあんま役立ってない説か。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aad",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aae",
      "text": "言葉は、ときに刃のようにもなりますものね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aaf",
      "text": "ですから私は、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ab0",
      "text": "「勝つための議論」よりも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ab1",
      "text": "「共に考えるための会話」が好きです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ab2",
      "text": "たとえば本を読んでいると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ab3",
      "text": "異なる思想の人物が、長い時間をかけて互いを理解していく物語に出会います。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ab4",
      "text": "そういう歩みは、とても静かですが、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ab5",
      "text": "人の心を変える力を持っているように感じます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ab6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ab7",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ab8",
      "text": "補足する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ab9",
      "text": "原理主義へのカウンターとして、研究者がよく挙げる要因は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aba",
      "text": " 1. [多元的接触]（contact hypothesis）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284abb",
      "text": " 2. [批判的思考教育]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284abc",
      "text": " 3. [情報リテラシー]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284abd",
      "text": "「異なる人と交流する機会」が増えるほど、極端な思想は弱まりやすい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284abe",
      "text": "参考:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284abf",
      "text": "https://greatergood.berkeley.edu/article/item/what_is_the_contact_hypothesis",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ac0",
      "text": "要点を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ac1",
      "text": "原理主義への対抗策は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ac2",
      "text": " 1. いきなり否定しない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ac3",
      "text": " 2. 対話の場を作る",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ac4",
      "text": " 3. 多様な人と接触する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ac5",
      "text": " 4. 情報の見方を学ぶ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ac6",
      "text": "この4つが基本。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ac7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ac8",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ac9",
      "text": "なるほどね〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aca",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284acb",
      "text": "「世界は一個じゃないよ」って体験が増えるほど、極端になりにくい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284acc",
      "text": "ってことか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284acd",
      "text": "ゲームでもあるよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ace",
      "text": "初心者の頃って",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284acf",
      "text": "「この戦法が最強！！」って思いがちだけど、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ad0",
      "text": "上手い人といっぱい対戦すると",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ad1",
      "text": "「いや、状況で変わるわ…」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ad2",
      "text": "ってなるやつｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ad3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ad4",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ad5",
      "text": "それはとても素敵なたとえですわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ad6",
      "text": "人生も、まるで物語や遊戯のように、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ad7",
      "text": "さまざまな選択肢が重なって進んでいくものなのでしょうね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ad8",
      "text": "ひとつの答えだけが世界を支配することは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ad9",
      "text": "おそらくないのだと思います。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ada",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284adb",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284adc",
      "text": "結論を簡潔に。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284add",
      "text": "原理主義の問題は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ade",
      "text": "「[唯一の正解]」という思考の固定化。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284adf",
      "text": "それへのカウンターは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ae0",
      "text": "複数の視点を持てる環境。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ae1",
      "text": "対話、教育、交流。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ae2",
      "text": "この三つが実装可能なアプローチだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ae3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ae4",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ae5",
      "text": "よし今日のまとめいくよー！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ae6",
      "text": "ふーこ的まとめ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ae7",
      "text": " 「それ絶対！」って思考は誰でもハマる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ae8",
      "text": " でも否定でぶつかると逆効果なこと多い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284ae9",
      "text": " いろんな人と話したり経験すると視野広がる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aea",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aeb",
      "text": "世界は思ったより広い、って気づくのが一番のカウンター！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aec",
      "text": "って感じかな？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aed",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aee",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284aef",
      "text": "ええ、とてもあたたかなまとめです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284af0",
      "text": "人の心が少しでも柔らかくなるなら、それはきっと良い道なのでしょうね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284af1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284af2",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284af3",
      "text": "同意。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284af4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284af5",
      "text": "議論終了。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284af6",
      "text": "また次のテーマで。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df30000000000284af7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350388,
      "updated": 1773350388
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df50000000000284af8",
      "text": "#2026-03-13",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350390,
      "updated": 1773350402
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32df70000000000284af9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350391,
      "updated": 1773350391
    }
  ]
}